# <type>(<scope>): <description>
#
# [optional body]
#
# [optional footer(s)]
#
# --- Typen ---
# feat:     Neues Feature
# fix:      Bugfix
# docs:     Nur Dokumentation
# style:    Formatting, kein Code-Change
# refactor: Weder Feature noch Fix
# test:     Tests hinzufuegen oder korrigieren
# chore:    Build, CI, Dependencies, Tooling
# perf:     Performance-Verbesserung
#
# --- Scopes (optional) ---
# checker, sanitizer, metrics, cli, io, models
#
# --- Regeln ---
# - Subject im Imperativ, kleingeschrieben, ohne Punkt am Ende
# - Subject max. 72 Zeichen
# - Body: Was und Warum, nicht Wie
# - Breaking Changes: Footer "BREAKING CHANGE: ..." oder "!" nach Type
#
# --- Beispiele ---
# feat(checker): add rule for repeated words
# fix(sanitizer): preserve tabs in code blocks
# docs: update README with usage examples
# chore: bump ftfy to 6.2
# feat(cli)!: rename ms-lint to ms-check
